OL,3,CThousands more social homes to be
OL,4,Cbuilt in the Midlands under new Mayor
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FITV News Central can exclusively
OL,8,Freveal the West Midlands Mayor's plans
OL,9,Fto kickstart one of the biggest social
OL,10,Fhousing programmes in decades.
OL,12,FRichard Parker has set a target of
OL,13,Fbuilding 20,000 new social homes over
OL,14,Fthe next 10 years in a bid to tackle
OL,15,Fthe region's affordable housing
OL,16,Fshortage.
OL,18,FSpeaking at a new site for 124 social
OL,19,Fand affordable homes in Edgbaston in
OL,20,FBirmingham, Parker said the need to
OL,21,Fbuild was urgent.
