OL,3,CThousands more social homes to be
OL,4,Cbuilt in the Midlands under new Mayor
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FHe said: "Across this region we've got
OL,8,Fover 60,000 people on waiting lists
OL,9,Ffor housing and we've got 6,500
OL,10,Ffamilies with 13,000 children living
OL,11,Fin high-cost, low-quality insecure,
OL,12,Ftemporary accommodation."
OL,14,F"Giving them homes like this is going
OL,15,Fto give them the base and security
OL,16,Fthey need so that they can prosper and
OL,17,Fmake a success of their lives."
