OL,3,CThousands more social homes to be
OL,4,Cbuilt in the Midlands under new Mayor
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FThe move to build more social homes is
OL,8,Fpartly down to the fact that, from
OL,9,Fnext year, the West Midlands mayor
OL,10,Fwill have a leading role in the use of
OL,11,Fgovernment money to build more social
OL,12,Fhomes.
OL,14,FIt will mean he has the funding to
OL,15,Funlock more derelict sites across the
OL,16,Fregion, including a multi-million-
OL,17,Fpound residential tower scheme in
OL,18,FDigbeth, Birmingham which will see 55%
OL,19,Fof the new properties classed as
OL,20,Faffordable with 141 being social homes
OL,21,Ffor rent and 127 for shared ownership.
