OL,3,CThousands more social homes to be
OL,4,Cbuilt in the Midlands under new Mayor
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FThe plans come after Birmingham City
OL,8,FCouncil moved to abandon its
OL,9,Faffordable housing target - enabling
OL,10,Fhouse builders to make more money on
OL,11,Ftheir developments.
OL,13,FOne person to have benefitted from a
OL,14,Fnew social home in Sanita Kaur Singh -
OL,15,Fshe has spent more than 20 years
OL,16,Fmoving between temporary accommodation
OL,17,Fto try to escape an abusive ex partner.
