OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FShe adds: "When I stepped into this
OL,8,Fnew place I was just so overwhelmed
OL,9,Fand I just cried happy tears and then
OL,10,Fwhen my children saw it they thought I
OL,11,Fwas lying and they just couldn't
OL,12,Fbelieve it."
OL,14,FSocial homes are designed to be more
OL,15,Faffordable than privately rented ones.
OL,17,FNowadays they are built with a much
OL,18,Fbigger focus on energy efficiency and
OL,19,Fthe keeping the cost of bills down.
